## Re-thinking data
<hr>
<p style="text-align: center;">How we've interacted with data dictates how we structure data mentally.</p>

<img src="images/excelScreenshot.jpg" 
	title="excel screenshot"
	alt = "Screenshot of microsoft excel window"
	border="0"
	style= "
	      display: block;
